  author      = "Jack, William and Suri, Tavneet",
  abstract    = "Mobile money is a tool that allows individuals to make
                 financial transactions using cell phone technology. In this
                 paper, we report initial results of two rounds of a large
                 survey of households in Kenya, the country that has seen
                 perhaps the most rapid and widespread growth of a mobile money
                 product - known locally as M‐PESA - in the developing world.
